### Italian
I file HTML sono generati dinamicamente via gulp con i task fileinclude-ios 
(directory www) e fileinclude-android (directory merges/android).
L'editing del codice HTML va fatto nella directory templates, utilizzando la
sintassi di gulp-file-include.
Ci√≥ consente di avere del codice comune per android ed ios, mentre le differenze
sono gestite a livello di template.

gulp watch monitora sia la directory templates che la directory www, propagando
le modifiche alla platform browser (versione ios) ed alle merges per Android.

### English
HTML files are dynamically generated via gulp with fileinclude-ios tasks (www 
directory) and fileinclude-android (merges/android directory).
HTML code editing is done in the templates directory, using the gulp-file-include
syntax.
This allows you to have the common code for android and ios, while the differences
are managed at template level.

gulp watch monitors both *templates* and *www* directory, propagating changes to
the browser platform (ios version) and android merges.